S0Gl0P 39?

38
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:40,118
- Halo?
- Stani.

39
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:01,077
Ti si pocasni gost.

40
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,991
Um...

41
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:10,635
Trebalo ti je duze nego sto sam ocekivao.
Cekali smo na tebe.

42
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:13,593
